Union Bank of Switzerland NV is issuinga 15 billion yen eurobond due June 1, 1992 paying 4-3/8 pct andpriced at 101-3/8 pct, lead manager Union Bank of Switzerland(Securities) Ltd said.    The issue has a call option and put option after four yearsat par and is guaranteed by Union Bank of Switzerland. Theselling concession is one pct while management and underwritingcombined pays 5/8 pct.    The issue is available in denominations of one mln yen andwill be listed in Luxembourg. The payment date is June 1. REUTER&#3;